  "verification_notes": "Ryan Odom completed his first season (2025-26) as Virginia head coach after being hired March 22, 2025. Cavaliers finished 30-6 (15-3 ACC, 2nd in conference) and earned a 3-seed in the NCAA Tournament Midwest region; beat Wright State in First Round, lost to 6-seed Tennessee in Second Round. Roster shown is 2025-26 season-end roster. The playing surface at John Paul Jones Arena was officially named 'Tony Bennett Court' on February 21, 2026. Owen Odom is the head coach's son. Ryan Odom's career head coaching record across all programs (UMBC, Utah State, VCU, Virginia) not verified — left null. 2026-27 schedule TBD. New seating plan begins 2027-28 season.",
